&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative &amp;amp; Scrappy:&lt;/strong&gt; You can see the angle that others miss. You understand how to frame a value proposition not just to a user, but to a partner looking to monetize their influence.&lt;/li&gt;
